  <div data-hf-id="hf-m2dp" id="cap0" class="clip cap" data-start="0.000" data-duration="2.517" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-aq83" class="txt">Yeah, it's something I'm actively trying to work on.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-r360" class="seg">1 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-wks8" id="cap1" class="clip cap" data-start="2.520" data-duration="9.997" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-gp9i" class="txt">I don't want to tie my identity and self-worth to how much I get accomplished on any given day. And it's hard, because I know that if I focus and I'm productive, I can</span><span data-hf-id="hf-2per" class="seg">2 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-lbcf" id="cap2" class="clip cap" data-start="12.520" data-duration="21.057" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-nm6v" class="txt">move things forward — whether it's business, content, or one day, I don't know, helping change the world. And it almost makes you feel like, unless you're working or utilizing the gift that the universe, God, gave you — you're not worth anything.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-zzau" class="seg">3 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-oziq" id="cap3" class="clip cap" data-start="33.580" data-duration="7.377" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-z9xo" class="txt">And so I'm trying to root my self-worth and identity in things beyond just my productivity.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-qu61" class="seg">4 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-kiab" id="cap4" class="clip cap" data-start="40.960" data-duration="3.977" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-a0hb" class="txt">Which is difficult, because I love working so much.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-du4s" class="seg">5 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-nxcj" id="cap5" class="clip cap" data-start="44.940" data-duration="3.297" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-vojz" class="txt">My bad day starts from when I don't get enough sleep.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-ivif" class="seg">6 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-ez4g" id="cap6" class="clip cap" data-start="48.240" data-duration="4.697" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-k5h7" class="txt">If I don't get enough sleep, I have a terrible day. It doesn't matter what happens that day.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-lqca" class="seg">7 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-d47u" id="cap7" class="clip cap" data-start="52.940" data-duration="3.837" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-biyq" class="txt">And usually I have incredible days when I get enough sleep.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-cij1" class="seg">8 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-t2gn" id="cap8" class="clip cap" data-start="56.780" data-duration="4.597" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-blh0" class="txt">And when I get things done in the morning before I have my deep work block in the afternoon.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-723k" class="seg">9 / 11</span></div>
  <div data-hf-id="hf-dz1w" id="cap9" class="clip cap" data-start="61.380" data-duration="6.757" data-track-index="2"><span data-hf-id="hf-e2ix" class="txt">And I have bad days when I eat oily food, don't stick to my diet, or miss a workout.</span><span data-hf-id="hf-dm32" class="seg">10 / 11</span></div>
